    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-12-22T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-12-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="237"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d237">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Acting President of Ecuador</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-12-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 22, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Having learned with deep regret of the death of President Estrada, I beg your
                    excellency to accept the expression of my profound sympathy and that of the
                    Government and people of the United States in the loss which you and the
                    Ecuadorian nation have sustained in the death of a statesman whose lofty and
                    patriotic purposes could not but merit and gain my appreciation. I should be
                    thankful to your excellency if you would be so good as to convey to Madam
                    Estrada the expression of personal sympathy of Mrs. Taft and myself in her
                    bereavement.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Taft.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
